2002-11-25 15:52  David Wheeler <david@wheeler.net>

	* Pg.pm, Pg.xs, dbdimp.c, t/01constants.t: Added constants for
	common PostgreSQL data types, plus simple tests to make sure that
	they work. These are exportable via "use DBD::Pg qw(:pg_types);".
	Documented deprecatation of the undocumented (and invalid) use of
	SQL_BINARY in bind_param() and documented the correct approach:
	"bind_param($num, $val { pg_type => PG_BYTEA });". Removed invalid
	(and broken) support for SQL_BINARY in quote().

